00:02:26.275 --> 00:02:28.828
Five fewer than eight stamps.

00:02:28.828 --> 00:02:30.290
And so we could write that.

00:02:30.290 --> 00:02:31.150
If we have eight stamps

00:02:31.151 --> 00:02:33.681
