00:03:10.620 --> 00:03:12.061
four, five.

00:03:12.061 --> 00:03:14.244
And what are you going to be left with?

00:03:14.244 --> 00:03:15.786
Well you're going to be left with

00:03:15.786 --> 00:03:18.123
